<dl id="n40094c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40094c">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40094c"> 94(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> you, the / counsellor etc</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Ho thou excellent companion, the generous, the ingenious, the judicious, the sagaceous, the Sage, my Secretary and my Minister and the Concealer of my secrets and the Councillor of my Kingdom. <small> Richard F. Burton, trans. <a name="RFBS" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#RFBS"><cite title="source">Supplemental Nights to the Book of the Thousand Nights and a Night with Notes Anthropological and Explanatory</cite></a> (n.d.) xvi.3</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
